    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0893a04"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>荊州國昌寺<persName key="A008830">行覺</persName>傳（<persName key="A013899">皓玉</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0893a05"/><persName key="A008830">釋行覺</persName>，姓劉氏，<placeName key="PL000000001981">鉅鹿</placeName>人也。穉歲英敏，立不易<lb
ed="T" n="0893a06"/>方，負志出家，親難沮勸。早投本部<placeName key="PL000000027756">永泰伽<lb
ed="T" n="0893a07"/>藍</placeName>，受業納戒。後於<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛都</placeName>遇<persName key="A005612">會禪師</persName>開悟玄<lb
ed="T" n="0893a08"/>理，秉心矯跡。遊方見<placeName key="PL000000027764">江陵</placeName>古寺，殿宇摧墮，<lb
ed="T" n="0893a09"/>闃而無人。<persName key="A008830">覺</persName>卸囊挂錫。明日，見樵夫驚怪，<lb
ed="T" n="0893a10"/>言「此是<placeName key="PL000000027841">國昌寺</placeName>，廢已三周。」將知人事相因，道<lb
ed="T" n="0893a11"/>從緣會，學者至矣，鄉人來矣，欝成一寺。時<lb
ed="T" n="0893a12"/>節使<persName key="A013900">崔尚書</persName>請召入城，謝而不赴。<anchor xml:id="beg0893002"/>檀<anchor xml:id="end0893002"/>施繼<lb
ed="T" n="0893a13"/>臻，乃興盛化。<date key="j20129332013286" notAfter-iso="0800-02-02" notBefore-iso="0799-02-14">貞元十五年</date>告終，年九十二。<lb
ed="T" n="0893a14"/><placeName key="PL000000023022">荊楚</placeName>之人營塔焉。又<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽山</placeName><persName key="A013899">釋皓玉</persName>者，趙氏<lb
ed="T" n="0893a15"/>之子，<placeName key="PL000000004129">上黨</placeName>人也。出塵于法清寺<!--找不到此地-->，後於<persName key="A005612">荷澤會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0893a16"/>下，大明心印，入<placeName key="PL000000028928">嶽</placeName>中蘭若養道。<placeName key="PL000000028913">衡陽</placeName>太守<lb
ed="T" n="0893a17"/><persName key="A013901">王展</persName>員外傾重。終時年八十餘，<date key="j20074402007823" notAfter-iso="0785" notBefore-iso="0784">興元中</date>入塔<lb
ed="T" n="0893a18"/>云。</p>
